<rdg wit="#L" n="a">radere quam penetrare </rdg>
<rdg wit="#L" n="b">globulum tapetis aut marmoris superficiem
										radere, quam lumen ipsam perspicui <app>
<rdg wit="#L" n="aa">densitatem </rdg>
<rdg wit="#L" n="bb">crassitiem penetrare; manifestum
												utique est refractiones non pro villositatum sed
												densitatum ratione variare. <app>
<rdg wit="#L" n="aaa">Quis neget villosio </rdg>
<rdg wit="#L" n="bbb">Nemo credo negabit oleum
												esse aer e villosius seu tenacius, at tamen lumen
												magis in oleo quam aere refringitur ad
												perpendicularem. </rdg>
</app>
</rdg>
</app>
</rdg>
</app>
</rdg>
<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> Nam <seg type="apparat-ellipsis"/>
 crassities. <hi rendition="#i">L</hi>
</rdg>
</app>
</p>
<p xml:id="Ch21.S1.p12">
<pb type="L"/>
<fw type="folNum">[97 v<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi>]
</fw> Nam etsi corporis duri politi
						superficies facilius radatur, quam mollis rugosi; non tamen facilius
						penetratur <anchor xml:id="satisfecitend"/>
crassities. <app type="Bfootnote">
<lem type="main">Quod enim</lem>
<note type="lemma-abbrev">crassities.</note>
<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> Nam </rdg>
<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> Quod enim <hi rendition="#i">L</hi>
</rdg>
</app> globus aliquis plumbeus tormento projectus saccum laneum non rumpit,
						ratio est, quia impetus ejus semel in materia molli perditus, nullo novo
						reparatur, quod secus est in <app type="Bfootnote">
<lem type="main">lumine</lem>
<note type="lemma-abbrev">in</note>
<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> flumine </rdg>
<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> lumine <hi rendition="#i">L</hi>
</rdg>
</app>, cujus fluxus est continuus. Ergo refractio<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
<term>refractio</term>
</index> in medio densiore ad perpendicularem, potius in aliis corporibus
						quam in lumine evenire deberet. <app type="Bfootnote">
<lem type="main">Si lumen difficilius iter in aere quam aqua
								invenit</lem>
<note type="lemma-abbrev">deberet.</note>
